- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) is a possible category as the paper discusses the application of a relatively new formalism (HASL) to a specific problem.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper may involve the implementation of the formalism in a programming language.
- cs.MS (Mathematical Software) is a possible category as the paper may involve the use of software tools for statistical model checking.
